hands_on_practices.solution:
我们从振荡开始时的已知比值出发，
$$
\frac{n_B}{\rho_\phi}
=\mathcal{K}\,\frac{b_\Phi|A|\sin(\delta_A)}{m_\phi^3}
\Bigl(\frac{\phi_{osc}}{M_{Pl}}\Bigr)^{\,n-2}\,.
$$
使用关系式
$$
\Bigl(\frac{\phi_{osc}}{M_{Pl}}\Bigr)^{2n-4}
=\frac{c}{C_D(n-1)}\Bigl(\frac{m_\phi}{M_{Pl}}\Bigr)^2\frac{1}{|\lambda|^2}\,,
$$
我们解出 $(\phi_{osc}/M_{Pl})^{\,n-2}$：
$$
\Bigl(\frac{\phi_{osc}}{M_{Pl}}\Bigr)^{\,n-2}
=\Bigl[\frac{c}{C_D(n-1)}\Bigr]^{\!\tfrac{1}{2}}
\Bigl(\frac{m_\phi}{M_{Pl}}\Bigr)\frac{1}{|\lambda|}\,.
$$
代回得到
$$
\frac{n_B}{\rho_\phi}
=\mathcal{K}\,\frac{b_\Phi|A|\sin(\delta_A)}{m_\phi^3}
\Bigl[\frac{c}{C_D(n-1)}\Bigr]^{\!\tfrac12}
\frac{m_\phi}{M_{Pl}}\frac{1}{|\lambda|}
=\mathcal{K}\,b_\Phi|A|\sin(\delta_A)\,
\frac{1}{|\lambda|\,m_\phi^2\,M_{Pl}}\,
\sqrt{\frac{c}{C_D(n-1)}}\,.
$$
当凝聚体衰变并再加热到 $T_{rh}$ 时，其能量密度变为
$\rho_{rad}=(\pi^2/30)g_*T_{rh}^4$，而熵密度为
$s=(2\pi^2/45)g_*T_{rh}^3$。因此
$$
\frac{\rho_\phi}{s}
=\frac{\frac{\pi^2}{30}g_*T_{rh}^4}{\frac{2\pi^2}{45}g_*T_{rh}^3}
=\frac{45}{60}T_{rh}=\frac{3}{4}T_{rh}\,.
$$
因此，最终的重子-熵比是
$$
Y_B=\frac{n_B}{s}
=\frac{n_B}{\rho_\phi}\,\frac{\rho_\phi}{s}
=\frac{3}{4}T_{rh}\,
\mathcal{K}\,b_\Phi|A|\sin(\delta_A)\,
\frac{1}{|\lambda|\,m_\phi^2\,M_{Pl}}
\sqrt{\frac{c}{C_D(n-1)}}\,.
$$
